{"type":"message","id":"f581bf4e","parentId":"481f0fe3","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:18:23.951Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 07:09 GMT+1] You are managing Z.E Digital Tech (@zedigitaltech) on X/Twitter.\n\n**Task:** Create 25 engaging posts about hotel technology and AI innovation.\n\n**Browser setup:** Use the `openclaw` browser profile (already logged in to @zedigitaltech).\n\n**Post pattern:**\n1. Navigate to: `https://x.com/compose/post`\n2. Type the post (max 280 chars!)\n3. Click \"Post\" button\n\n**Content themes:**\n\nHot Takes:\n- \"The hotel industry is 10 years behind on tech. Time to catch up.\"\n- \"Voice-first is the new mobile-first. Hotels take note.\"\n- \"Guest expectations changed forever post-2020. Adapt or lose.\"\n\nFun/Light:\n- \"POV: You're a hotel guest and AI just handled your 2am request instantly\"\n- \"Hotels with bad wifi be like: 'We value your stay' 😅\"\n- \"Friday feeling: When your AI handles all the routine questions\"\n\nIndustry News Commentary:\n- React to AI trends\n- Comment on tech developments\n- Share opinions on hospitality news\n\n**IMPORTANT:**\n- Keep ALL posts under 280 characters\n- Track how many you successfully posted\n- Report final count when done"}],"timestamp":1772432303949}}
