25 X posts cannot be completed in the current state due to these technical limitations.\n\n**Posts ready to publish (if browser was working):**\nI had prepared to create 25 engaging posts about hotel technology and AI innovation covering:\n- Hot takes about hotel tech gaps\n- Fun/light content about AI in hospitality  \n- Industry news commentary\n- Voice-first technology trends\n- Guest experience improvements\n\nAll posts would have been under 280 characters as requested."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zhipu","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":259,"output":424,"cacheRead":84352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772432707914}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"15361cf2","parentId":"e954375a","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:26:05.807Z","summary":"No prior history.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser requested creation of 25 engaging X/Twitter posts about hotel technology and AI innovation for the account @zedigitaltech, using the `openclaw` browser profile. Posts should be under 280 characters and cover themes: Hot Takes, Fun/Light content, and Industry News Commentary.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Confirmed browser is running with openclaw profile (Chrome, port 9222)\n- Navigated to x.com/compose/post\n- Encountered multiple \"follow suggestion\" popups that redirected the page when dismissed\n- Eventually reached the compose dialog with a text input field\n- A draft already exists in the textbox: \"Hot take: Hotels without AI assistants will feel like landlines by 2027. The future is conversational.\" with hashtags and emojis\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- The compose dialog is open with textbox (ref=e82) active\n- Post button is ref=e175\n- Content themes provided include:\n  - Hot Takes: \"The hotel industry is 10 years behind on tech. Time to catch up.\"\n  - Fun/Light: \"POV: You're a hotel guest and AI just handled your 2am request instantly\"\n  - Industry News Commentary about AI trends and hospitality tech\n- Task is to create 25 posts total, tracking successful posts\n- Browser refs are expiring quickly between actions, requiring fresh snapshots frequently","firstKeptEntryId":"28baa504","tokensBefore":85035,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
